profile:
At Powerclean we know that first impressions count.  Wether you are selling your home, or are looking to retain its value, increasing your curb appeal will set  your residence above the rest.  

We know deep cleaning is hard, but that's how we like it.  Our pressure washers and years of property maintenance experience will eliminate any stain on your driveway, that mildew on your deck and the 20 years of dirt collecting on your brick facade.  

The earth is our best pal, so we do everything we can to help her out.  Pressure washing is the most environmentally friendly way to restore hard surfaces, and that's why it's our chosen method for cleaning.  Chemicals? - nope. Bleach? - no way.  We won't use any product that doesn't biodegrade.  After all, part of increasing your curb appeal is protecting the environment around it.

Contact us through email, or via phone and we'll come by to meet you and your home.  We will take a walk around your property, assess your unique needs, and create a fully customized estimate free of charge.   

Customer service is our biggest asset and exceeding your expectations is our highest priority.
